Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久疏战阵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个水平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了吗 吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有言在先 别想对我指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的都是防守基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只关心能不能和高达交手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你的个人复仇舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢 你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一的话没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 是我的菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想去讨好杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在执行长官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 该早点收拾了它才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 这边交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识下 对联邦绝望的人的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正与AGE-FX交战的机体属于联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机师资料 显示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被派往月神基地的王牌机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德 本来是男性的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 她是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要 用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特他 并不是为了拯救维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须听你的疯言疯语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特想 只留下优秀的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想亲手 在联邦和维甘中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行种群选拔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算为这种人卖命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒醒 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说到这份上还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这点本事吗 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前是联邦的机师对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又…怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的话 应该清楚联邦和维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两方战斗的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你 和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是烦透了联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦透了那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满脑子只有明哲保身的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么让你变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根上校的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背景调查资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就传送
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论过去如何 她现在投身维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的敌人这一点不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-1的强化改造马上就将完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等离子潜航导弹的准备工作不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 这场仗只有胜没有败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开着老机体口气还不小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 吉拉德过去有过啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她 真正的名字
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜·斯普里根曾经是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶研制中机动战士的试飞员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一次 发生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我 你到底遇到了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和联邦没什么话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你 怎么可能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,评价试飞辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜·斯普里根少校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射器的点火机关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还要调整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头我会整理成报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天状态还行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 比不上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们作为同期机师相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相切磋进步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受着属于二人的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 久等了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好久好久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时觉得 做试飞员也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得是因为当了试飞员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蕾娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉梦想也不再那么遥不可及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有温馨家庭的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为未来许下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用来增幅你们X-Rounder能力的新系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下只需要收集实际数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行最终调整
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个已经通过了军方安全基准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情施展一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们前往进行测试飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 启动新系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 提高功率
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗奈尔呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不听使唤 请求中止测试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯普里根呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统失控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法控制动力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能下床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 跟我回病房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他呢 弗奈尔少校在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我 活了下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 我得知了事故真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管 提高输出功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上头的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统…失控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们急于…获得成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是他的操纵失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他的死深表同情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是报告上说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的死是源于未按指示操纵系统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从今日起特别连升两级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任命你为上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我当个哑巴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是出去乱说 最终对你也没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候 我也保不住你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保全新系统项目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以他的个人清白为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相被掩盖了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他约定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被对联邦的憎恨代替
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了复仇义无反顾抛弃联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回应了维甘的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的战斗不会有任何结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该用在这种事上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 说什么天真烂漫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份力量就是为战斗而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为完成复仇而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用这份力量 阻止战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的机体跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没拜托你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杰哈特大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人他不会抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一个部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在你心目中他是这么好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只说他是个值得尊敬的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊敬？就这么简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想为杰哈特大人出力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,助他开辟维甘光明的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少做美梦为好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生才不会像你想得这么一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘必须被歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德小姐一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有要离开联邦的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不是联邦的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在联邦 已经不存在名叫蕾娜·斯普里根的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我不是蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不能下床
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 跟我回病房
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他呢 弗奈尔少校在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少校他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·弗奈尔少校已经
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他始终和我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫吉拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 吉拉德·斯普里根
